Maintainer: Julien Brun <brun@nceas.ucsb.edu>
Description: Primary functionality is to take a list of Huc8's and retrieve data from the CAMELS model output for those hucs  
    More specifically these functions retrieve: daymet mean forcing, stream gauge, name, geology, topology, vegetation, hydrology, soils and climate data.
    Additionally, there is a function tying this data to water quality data from the dataRetrieval package
